    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Kisaragi Clan, level 8+ <br /><strong>Description:</strong> You master the Kisaragi style of bladework, culminating in a form of it unique to your justice. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>When casting a Kisaragi Clan Hijutsu while under the effect of Chain, you may immediately move up to 15 feet without expending your movement before the effects of the jutsu, or after.</li><li>Select up to 2 jutsu you currently have learned, and grant them the <em><strong>Hijutsu</strong></em> and <em><strong>Chain X </strong></em>keywords. Jutsu granted the <em><strong>Hijutsu</strong></em> and <em><strong>Chain X</strong></em> keyword this way are considered Kisaragi Clan Hijutsu.</li><li><p>When you would cast a Kisaragi Clan Hijutsu which has no additional effects when cast as a Chain 2, or Chain 3, they gain the following effects;</p><ul><li><em><strong>Chain 2</strong></em>: Increase the die step of this jutsu by 1</li><li><em><strong>Chain 3</strong></em>: Gain 1 Heat Point.</li></ul></li></ul><p></p>",
